        {
            "title": "美對沖基金Capstone 擬關閉香港辦事處",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美對沖基金Capstone 擬關閉香港辦事處\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cg_Rbi.ANTasaTXPwiaHGQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-03/106375c0-e1e8-11ee-afdf-e93aceb3afbd\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美對沖基金Capstone 擬關閉香港辦事處</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%8D%E6%B2%96%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91capstone-%E6%93%AC%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E8%99%95-183300467.html",
